<P>
   RUSSIA-CLINTON-ASSESS (Moscow) _ Seeking to lower expectations
Clinton administration officials had insisted this should not be
viewed as an arms control summit. But it was. By Michael R. Gordon.
</P>
<P>
   LEBANON-DIVISIONS (Kafr Shuba, Lebanon) _ Across the
nine-mile-wide border strip that Israel claimed as its security
zone in 1985, every village and town has its tales of divided
families and estranged neighbors, of a household that made its
accommodation to the occupation while the one next door persisted
in stubborn resistance. By Susan Sachs.
</P>
<P>
   BRITAIN-ROYALS (London) _ Queen Elizabeth II and Camilla Parker
Bowles met this weekend for the first time, setting off speculation
across Britain over a possible marriage for Prince Charles. By
