</P>
<P>
   GROUCHO-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ In ``Groucho: The Life and Times
of Julius Henry Marx,'' Stefan Kanfer does a nimble job of tracing
the outlines of Groucho Marx's life and the evolution of his antic
art. Reviewed by Michiko Kakutani.
</P>
