<HEADER>
A5171 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1S     06-05 0486
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Monday, June 5, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
