<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-05 17:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5253 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r a BC-WAR-BRIDE-HNS &LR;      06-05 0753
