Zachary, 9, right, and Nicholas, 4. (Ozier Muhammad/The New York
Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT306) FORT KNOX, Ky. -- June 5, 2000 -- RACE-MILITARY-6 -- In
a military that calls itself colorblind, two sergeants see race
