Race Is Lived in America.'' U.S. newspaper clients of the New York
Times News Service, who do not subscribe to the photo service, can
make individual purchases of photos with this series at a special
price of $100 per image. Thumbnails can be viewed at the News
Service site on Presslink, Newscom and at the Weick Database.
